::KitKat::

She looked at Drillbit,"Go and make sure the mouse on the bridge 
doesn't mess things up," she said with a smirk. "I'll be right there 
as soon as I'm done with these two."

She turned to Gabriel."Your honored to see me? You must have a wire 
loose in your logic circuits." She chuckled. She hadn't laughed in a 
long time and it felt good to laugh. "I'm pleased to meet you too. 
What can I do for you? Come, let's go to the meeting room and we can 
talk there." She let them to the conference room next to the bridge.


Darkmouse::
She sat in the captains chair, with her feet up on the console and 
sipping on a tall glass of lemonaide. "Hmm, yeah, this is the life."
